---
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
import { UserPlus, TvMinimalPlay } from "@lucide/astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import HeroImage from "@/assets/static/IMG_8393adj-topaz.avif";
---

<div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center md:gap-6 xl:gap-12">
    <div class="relative">
      <Image
        class="w-full rounded-md"
        src={HeroImage}
        format="avif"
        loading="lazy"
        width={800}
        height={600}
        alt="Hero Image"
      />
      <div
        class="from-primary via-card/0 to-primary absolute inset-0 -z-1 -ms-4 me-4 mt-4 -mb-4 size-full rounded-md bg-linear-to-tr lg:-ms-6 lg:me-6 lg:mt-6 lg:-mb-6"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h1
        class="block text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl lg:leading-tight"
      >
        Welcome to the <br /><span class="text-accent-5">Air War Trail</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-justify">
        If you walk along the air war trail today, you will see the remains of
        the wartime airfields everywhere you look. The images of war have grown
        faint, but the spirit of the bomber boys over East Anglia will never
        fade. They are all gone away now, these once busy and impressive places
        so vital so long ago. Now only the green fields blow in the wind, and
        the sounds of Flying Fortresses and Liberators along the taxiways have
        been silenced forever.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-justify">
        The Yanks are but memories now. Here and there only solitary walls rest
        on this hallowed ground, standing vigil across the landscape of time.
      </p>

      <div class="my-8 flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/subscribe">
          <Button size="lg" className="text-lg font-semibold">
            <UserPlus class="size-6" />
            Subscribe Now
          </Button>
        </a>
        <a href="/episodes">
          <Button
            variant="reversed"
            size="lg"
            className="text-lg font-semibold"
          >
            <TvMinimalPlay class="size-6" />
            View Latest Episode
          </Button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
